  "description": "A wide, expansive view of the ocean under a heavily overcast sky. The sea is a dark, choppy gray, reflecting little light. The sky is a pale, washed-out gray, creating a sense of muted light and a flat horizon. The sun, or a bright source of light, is obscured by the clouds, but a bright glow is visible in the center of the image. Several birds appear as dark silhouettes in the sky, adding a touch of life to the otherwise desolate scene. The water has a slight texture and visible wave patterns.",
